#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_pymotor.md:1
msgid "Deploy vLLM-Ascend with MindIE-PyMotor"
msgstr "使用 MindIE-PyMotor 部署 vLLM-Ascend"
#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_pymotor.md:3
msgid "1. Overview"
msgstr "1. 概述"
#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_pymotor.md:5
msgid ""
"[MindIE-PyMotor](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor) provides one-"
"click deployment for **prefill–decode (PD) disaggregation** and **PD "
"aggregation** on Ascend NPUs with vLLM-Ascend. It uses **high-performance "
"scheduling and load balancing**, together with **RAS (Reliability, "
"Availability and Serviceability) capabilities**, to build inference "
"services that are fast and highly stable."
msgstr ""
"[MindIE-PyMotor](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor) 在昇腾 NPU 上基于 "
"vLLM-Ascend 提供 **Prefill-Decode (PD) 分离** 与 **PD 聚合** 的一键部署能力，并通过 "
"**高性能调度与负载均衡**，以及 **RAS（可靠性、可用性与可维护性）能力**，构建高速且高稳定的推理服务。"
#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_pymotor.md:7
msgid "2. Getting Started"
msgstr "2. 快速开始"
#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_pymotor.md:9
msgid ""
"For quick deployment instructions, refer to the [MindIE-PyMotor Quick "
"Start](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor/blob/master/docs/zh/"
"user_guide/README.md)."
msgstr ""
"快速部署说明请参考 [MindIE-PyMotor 快速开始](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-"
"PyMotor/blob/master/docs/zh/user_guide/README.md)。"
